Exercice 5

a) P(A) = 4/52 = 1/13
   P(B) = 13/52 = 1/4
   P(A et B) = 1/52
   P(A)*P(B) = 1/13*1/4 = 1/52 => indépendant

b) P(A) = 3/51 = 1/17
   P(B) = 12/51 = 4/17
   P(A et B) = 0 != P(A)*P(B) => dépendant

